      "title": "Configuration standards for NSC rulesets are: • Defined. • Implemented. • Maintained. Customized App...",
      "statement": "Configuration standards for NSC rulesets are: • Defined. • Implemented. • Maintained. Customized Approach Objective The way that NSCs are configured and operate are defined and consistently applied.",
