      "title": "Audit logs for the anti-malware solution(s) are enabled and retained in accordance with Requirement ...",
      "statement": "Audit logs for the anti-malware solution(s) are enabled and retained in accordance with Requirement 10.5.1. Customized Approach Objective Historical records of anti-malware actions are immediately available and retained for at least 12 months.",
